{"tid":1966263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（天佑美國）紐約死亡連續3日創新高　挖壕啟動大型埋葬","createTime":"2020-04-10T05:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T02:46:41.000Z","uid":66087,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0db6c2db196f0f739b7b077e9530ee0b2d8d29ac","tid":1966263,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:11:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2615494/【美國疫情】紐約死亡連續3日創新高%20挖壕啟動大型埋葬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2615494%2F%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C3%E6%97%A5%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%2520%E6%8C%96%E5%A3%95%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%9F%8B%E8%91%AC&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6y%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=3c85e61e\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2615494/【美國疫情】紐約死亡連續3日創新高%20挖壕啟動大型埋葬</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDGfmMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDGfmMn.jpg&h=11b4e310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國疫情持續惡化，重災區紐約州的新冠肺炎死亡病例，連續3日創新高。紐約州過去24小時已錄得799宗死亡病例，累計逾7000人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n紐約市政府早前稱，會在哈特島（Hart Island）挖壕，臨時掩埋疫情死者，供家屬容後處理死者身後事。身穿防護裝備的工人周四（9日）將屍體埋在其中一條壕中。<br />\n<br />\n紐約市長白思豪（Bill de Blasio）指，雖然疫情難在4月緩解，但5月的情況可能好轉，屆時或考慮放寬部分防疫限制。惟科莫強調，所有時間點只是猜測，無人都能保證5月疫情好轉。<br />\n<br />\n截至4月9日，美國累計有46萬人確診感染新冠肺炎，超過1.6萬人死亡。"},{"pid":"24183b2f4a6134e73b5a38377f98f1a3d66a952c","tid":1966263,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"股市 gogogo"},{"pid":"c8e625dc0b9da6a14ad68e9ddf2d292b477ca465","tid":1966263,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"阻阻你<br />\n文宣要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［網軍召集］海外手足fb比五毛洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1966095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1966095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08f89daace9c6fecdbcd646da82bdb9f0555ee23","tid":1966263,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae855ad1f6c4c302f9adf847bd85426d10bc74d4","tid":1966263,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf38417147670445949a6b7d50d25539bb1266a","tid":1966263,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:16:42.000Z","msg":"呢舖一野打殘美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a87a4a4fb72a23e00cd901cbf1dbf27598ca63","tid":1966263,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"flu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\noverreact<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c463145bc42ca5aad7cdc8e8a769dac6e87508","tid":1966263,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"將來必十倍奉還！！"},{"pid":"e9a655374c1cf71a31e484f52550778d56009674","tid":1966263,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"希望美國同世界會打贏呢場生化戰爭<br />\n其望隱瞞疫情既集團全體被無人機擊殺<br />\n然後解體"},{"pid":"2d02b405e08d0ee2a5786f9e936fe12f42ced3eb","tid":1966263,"uid":164761,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020